'''Andy Johnson''' born [[14 June]], [[1974]] in [[Wigan]], [[Greater Manchester]], [[England]], is a former [[rugby league]] player.

Andy Johnson's position of choice was in the [[Rugby_league_positions#Second-row|second-row]] and comfortable in a number of other positions.

He played for [[Salford City Reds]], [[Castleford Tigers]], [[London Broncos]], [[Huddersfield Giants]], and [[Wigan Warriors]] in the [[Super League (Europe)|European Super League]].

